    "collapsible_text_YPVYyd": {
      "type": "collapsible-text",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "richtext": "<p>Are you looking for high-quality car mats? Are you considering purchasing the velour version? Or perhaps you will opt for professional car mats made of durable EVA material? Check out their benefits and advantages over velour. In our online and offline store, you will find unique car mats that not only accentuate the exceptional style of each vehicle but also ensure driving safety, user comfort, and ease of cleaning. Below, we will outline the basic features of car mats made of velour and compare traditional mats with our unique EVA products.</p>",
        "collapsible_richtext": "<p>Velour as a Material for Car mats<br/>Velour is a material that has been used for manufacturing car mats for many years. It is suitable for both cars with richer equipment and vehicles with traditional interiors. Drivers opt for velour mats especially because they are very easy to keep clean and they also look nice. To ensure that car mats made of velour last as long as possible, it is important to remember to care for them properly. Velour should not be exposed to sunlight as it can fade. Soft-bristled brushes should be used for cleaning. Traditional velour tolerates mild detergents well, but strong chemicals can cause it to discolor or deteriorate.</p>",
        "button_text_more": "Read more",
        "button_text_less": "Read less",
        "padding_top_mobile": 40,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 40,
        "padding_top": 50,
        "padding_bottom": 57
      }
    },
    "image_with_collapsible_text_XCLeBp": {
      "type": "image-with-collapsible-text",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Frame_234.png",
        "header": "<h2>What things <strong>should you pay attention to </strong>before choosing the right car mats?</h2>",
        "richtext": "<p>What is the difference between traditional velour and EVA products?<br/>First and foremost, the products available in our store are handmade. Therefore, they are perfectly tailored to fit the dimensions of the floor in your vehicle. We prioritize the quality of our mats, so we strive to ensure they are made with the highest precision. We use materials of very good quality for their production. Thanks to our mats, the standard of your car will never be the same again! Our goal is to improve not only comfort but also to keep the car clean.</p>",
        "collapsible_richtext": "<h3>What are the advantages of EVA mats compared to traditional velour products?</h3><p>EVA mats are lightweight and easy to remove from the vehicle. They are also very light, so nobody should have the slightest problem with removing them. Another characteristic is that EVA mats are odorless. However, let's focus on the fact that the products available in our store, EVA mats, are innovative and surpass traditional velour in quality. Firstly, regular velour mats do not precisely cover the vehicle's floor. On the other hand, EVA products are handmade, after careful examination of the full dimensions of the floor surface in the specific brand of vehicle, which ensures their precise fitting and coverage of the floor up to 99 percent. Moreover, EVA products do not absorb water, and any type of dirt is stored in them stably and does not spread throughout the interior of the vehicle. The situation is different with traditional velour mats—they absorb water and dirt, so entering the vehicle with muddy or wet shoes can cause dirt not only on the mat but also inside the vehicle.</p>",
        "button_text_more": "Read more",
        "button_text_less": "Read less",
        "padding_top_mobile": 40,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 40,
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80
      }
    },
    "text_with_image_zBPL3c": {
      "type": "text-with-image",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "image": "shopify://shop_images/Rectangle_91_1.png",
        "header": "<p><strong>WHAT ARE THE DIFFERENCES</strong> IN CLEANING EVA PRODUCTS AND VELOUR MATS?</p>",
        "richtext": "<p>Car mats made of velour are difficult to clean. Soft-bristled brushes should be used for their maintenance, and attention should be paid to the type of detergents used. EVA mats are easy to clean. Thanks to a special formula, they tolerate the use of even strong detergents. They also do not require specialized maintenance. Importantly, they can serve you for many years without losing their original appearance even after years of use. Traditional velour products, on the other hand, may undergo deformation and fading, altering their appearance. By choosing EVA products, you can match the interior of your car to your personality. We offer many different color variants of these car mats. With our products, you can be sure that car mats can add charm and elegance to any vehicle brand. The high quality of our products is confirmed by many positive reviews from satisfied customers.</p><p>In summary, EVA mats are characterized by much higher durability compared to their velour counterparts. They fit perfectly to the floor and are available in a diverse range of colors. EVA mats provide an excellent alternative to products made from other materials. Easy cleaning, precise fitting, and high durability ensure enjoyable usage. So, if you're looking for high-quality car mats, check out the EVAMATS brand offer. We also invite you to contact our store. We'll be happy to answer any questions and help you choose the best version of EVA mats.</p>",
        "padding_top_mobile": 40,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 40,
        "padding_top": 80,
        "padding_bottom": 80
      }
    },
    "richtext_section_K7WAxg": {
      "type": "richtext-section",
      "disabled": true,
      "settings": {
        "header": "<p>Why should you <strong>purchase mats from our store?</strong></p>",
        "richtext": "<p>By purchasing EVA mats in our store, you not only have a guarantee of excellent product quality but also fantastic prices. These are Polish articles, handcrafted. Therefore, we are confident that you will be satisfied when choosing EVA mats!</p>",
        "padding_top_mobile": 40,
        "padding_bottom_mobile": 40,
        "padding_top": 58,
        "padding_bottom": 57
      }
    },
